# Benchmarks of various Rust Entity Component Systems

## Benchmarks
Benchmarks are run on [Travis CI](https://travis-ci.org/lschmierer/ecs_bench/).

Benchmarks are located in `benches/[bench_name]_[ecs_crate_name].rs`.

